{
  "video_id": "9TPFLHvn024",
  "title": "Lisa Kristine: Photos that bear witness to modern slavery",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15723.0,
      "end_time": 22123.0,
      "text": "I'm 150 feet down an illegal mine shaft in Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 22123.0,
      "end_time": 26244.0,
      "text": "The air is thick with heat and dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 26244.0,
      "end_time": 29653.0,
      "text": "and it's hard to breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 29653.0,
      "end_time": 32915.0,
      "text": "I can feel the brush of sweaty bodies passing me"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 32915.0,
      "end_time": 37161.0,
      "text": "in the darkness, but I can't see much else."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 37161.0,
      "end_time": 41131.0,
      "text": "I hear voices talking, but mostly the shaft"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 41131.0,
      "end_time": 45119.0,
      "text": "is this cacophony of men coughing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 45119.0,
      "end_time": 49030.0,
      "text": "and stone being broken with primitive tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 49030.0,
      "end_time": 53085.0,
      "text": "Like the others, I wear a flickering, cheap flashlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 53085.0,
      "end_time": 57881.0,
      "text": "tied to my head with this elastic, tattered band,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 57881.0,
      "end_time": 61221.0,
      "text": "and I can barely make out the slick tree limbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 61221.0,
      "end_time": 64250.0,
      "text": "holding up the walls of the three-foot square hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 64250.0,
      "end_time": 68876.0,
      "text": "dropping hundreds of feet into the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 68876.0,
      "end_time": 71956.0,
      "text": "When my hand slips, I suddenly remember a miner"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 71956.0,
      "end_time": 76237.0,
      "text": "I had met days before who had lost his grip"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 76237.0,
      "end_time": 80858.0,
      "text": "and fell countless feet down that shaft."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 80858.0,
      "end_time": 83389.0,
      "text": "As I stand talking to you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 83389.0,
      "end_time": 86893.0,
      "text": "these men are still deep in that hole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 86893.0,
      "end_time": 90408.0,
      "text": "risking their lives without payment or compensation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 90408.0,
      "end_time": 93548.0,
      "text": "and often dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 93548.0,
      "end_time": 98736.0,
      "text": "I got to climb out of that hole, and I got to go home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 98736.0,
      "end_time": 104918.0,
      "text": "but they likely never will, because they're trapped in slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 104918.0,
      "end_time": 107825.0,
      "text": "For the last 28 years, I've been documenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 107825.0,
      "end_time": 110386.0,
      "text": "indigenous cultures in more than 70 countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 110386.0,
      "end_time": 114181.0,
      "text": "on six continents, and in 2009 I had the great honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 114181.0,
      "end_time": 118593.0,
      "text": "of being the sole exhibitor at the Vancouver Peace Summit."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 118593.0,
      "end_time": 122165.0,
      "text": "Amongst all the astonishing people I met there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 122165.0,
      "end_time": 125335.0,
      "text": "I met a supporter of Free the Slaves, an NGO"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 125335.0,
      "end_time": 130662.0,
      "text": "dedicated to eradicating modern day slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 130662.0,
      "end_time": 133551.0,
      "text": "We started talking about slavery, and really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 133551.0,
      "end_time": 136415.0,
      "text": "I started learning about slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 136415.0,
      "end_time": 139624.0,
      "text": "for I had certainly known it existed in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 139624.0,
      "end_time": 142635.0,
      "text": "but not to such a degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 142635.0,
      "end_time": 146378.0,
      "text": "After we finished talking, I felt so horrible"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 146378.0,
      "end_time": 149754.0,
      "text": "and honestly ashamed at my own lack of knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 149754.0,
      "end_time": 153264.0,
      "text": "of this atrocity in my own lifetime, and I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 153264.0,
      "end_time": 158132.0,
      "text": "if I don't know, how many other people don't know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 158132.0,
      "end_time": 161947.0,
      "text": "It started burning a hole in my stomach, so within weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 161947.0,
      "end_time": 164923.0,
      "text": "I flew down to Los Angeles to meet with the director"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 164923.0,
      "end_time": 168194.0,
      "text": "of Free the Slaves and offer them my help."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 168194.0,
      "end_time": 172764.0,
      "text": "Thus began my journey into modern day slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 172764.0,
      "end_time": 175906.0,
      "text": "Oddly, I had been to many of these places before."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 175906.0,
      "end_time": 179387.0,
      "text": "Some I even considered like my second home."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 179387.0,
      "end_time": 186822.0,
      "text": "But this time, I would see the skeletons hidden in the closet."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 186822.0,
      "end_time": 189127.0,
      "text": "A conservative estimate tells us there are more than"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 189127.0,
      "end_time": 193282.0,
      "text": "27 million people enslaved in the world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 193282.0,
      "end_time": 196762.0,
      "text": "That's double the amount of people taken from Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 196762.0,
      "end_time": 200887.0,
      "text": "during the entire trans-Atlantic slave trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 200887.0,
      "end_time": 204031.0,
      "text": "A hundred and fifty years ago, an agricultural slave"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 204031.0,
      "end_time": 207525.0,
      "text": "cost about three times the annual salary"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 207525.0,
      "end_time": 210271.0,
      "text": "of an American worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 210271.0,
      "end_time": 214264.0,
      "text": "That equates to about $50,000 in today's money."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 214264.0,
      "end_time": 218656.0,
      "text": "Yet today, entire families can be enslaved for generations"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 218656.0,
      "end_time": 223524.0,
      "text": "over a debt as small as $18."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 223524.0,
      "end_time": 226556.0,
      "text": "Astonishingly, slavery generates profits"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 226556.0,
      "end_time": 232302.0,
      "text": "of more than $13 billion worldwide each year."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 232302.0,
      "end_time": 235154.0,
      "text": "Many have been tricked by false promises"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 235154.0,
      "end_time": 239700.0,
      "text": "of a good education, a better job, only to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 239700.0,
      "end_time": 243208.0,
      "text": "that they're forced to work without pay"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 243208.0,
      "end_time": 248876.0,
      "text": "under the threat of violence, and they cannot walk away."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 248876.0,
      "end_time": 252158.0,
      "text": "Today's slavery is about commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 252158.0,
      "end_time": 256188.0,
      "text": "so the goods that enslaved people produce have value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 256188.0,
      "end_time": 261186.0,
      "text": "but the people producing them are disposable."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 261185.99999999997,
      "end_time": 265576.0,
      "text": "Slavery exists everywhere, nearly, in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 265576.0,
      "end_time": 272543.0,
      "text": "and yet it is illegal everywhere in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 272543.0,
      "end_time": 277333.0,
      "text": "In India and Nepal, I was introduced to the brick kilns."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 277333.0,
      "end_time": 280124.0,
      "text": "This strange and awesome sight was like"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 280124.0,
      "end_time": 284014.0,
      "text": "walking into ancient Egypt or Dante's Inferno."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 284014.0,
      "end_time": 288165.0,
      "text": "Enveloped in temperatures of 130 degrees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 288165.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "men, women, children, entire families in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295411.0,
      "text": "were cloaked in a heavy blanket of dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 295411.0,
      "end_time": 298031.0,
      "text": "while mechanically stacking bricks on their head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 298031.0,
      "end_time": 301152.0,
      "text": "up to 18 at a time, and carrying them"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 301152.0,
      "end_time": 306102.0,
      "text": "from the scorching kilns to trucks hundreds of yards away."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 306102.0,
      "end_time": 309629.0,
      "text": "Deadened by monotony and exhaustion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 309629.0,
      "end_time": 315214.0,
      "text": "they work silently, doing this task over and over"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 315214.0,
      "end_time": 318567.0,
      "text": "for 16 or 17 hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 318567.0,
      "end_time": 322286.0,
      "text": "There were no breaks for food, no water breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 322286.0,
      "end_time": 324838.0,
      "text": "and the severe dehydration made urinating"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 324838.0,
      "end_time": 327710.0,
      "text": "pretty much inconsequential."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 327710.0,
      "end_time": 330142.0,
      "text": "So pervasive was the heat and the dust"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 330142.0,
      "end_time": 333893.0,
      "text": "that my camera became too hot to even touch"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 333893.0,
      "end_time": 336345.0,
      "text": "and ceased working."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 336345.0,
      "end_time": 339117.0,
      "text": "Every 20 minutes, I'd have to run back to our cruiser"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 339117.0,
      "end_time": 342466.0,
      "text": "to clean out my gear and run it under an air conditioner"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 342466.0,
      "end_time": 345521.0,
      "text": "to revive it, and as I sat there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 345521.0,
      "end_time": 350131.0,
      "text": "I thought, my camera is getting far better treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 350131.0,
      "end_time": 352457.0,
      "text": "than these people."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 352457.0,
      "end_time": 355329.0,
      "text": "Back in the kilns, I wanted to cry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 355329.0,
      "end_time": 358507.0,
      "text": "but the abolitionist next to me quickly grabbed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 358507.0,
      "end_time": 362811.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Lisa, don't do that. Just don't do that here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 362811.0,
      "end_time": 366704.0,
      "text": "And he very clearly explained to me that emotional displays"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 366704.0,
      "end_time": 369238.0,
      "text": "are very dangerous in a place like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 369238.0,
      "end_time": 373092.0,
      "text": "not just for me, but for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 373092.0,
      "end_time": 376742.0,
      "text": "I couldn't offer them any direct help."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 376742.0,
      "end_time": 379535.0,
      "text": "I couldn't give them money, nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 379535.0,
      "end_time": 381332.0,
      "text": "I wasn't a citizen of that country."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 381332.0,
      "end_time": 384420.0,
      "text": "I could get them in a worse situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 384420.0,
      "end_time": 387200.0,
      "text": "than they were already in."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 387200.0,
      "end_time": 389456.0,
      "text": "I'd have to rely on Free the Slaves to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 389456.0,
      "end_time": 392298.0,
      "text": "within the system for their liberation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 392298.0,
      "end_time": 395767.0,
      "text": "and I trusted that they would."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 395767.0,
      "end_time": 399204.0,
      "text": "As for me, I'd have to wait until I got home"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 399204.0,
      "end_time": 403166.0,
      "text": "to really feel my heartbreak."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 403166.0,
      "end_time": 406039.0,
      "text": "In the Himalayas, I found children carrying stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 406039.0,
      "end_time": 408789.0,
      "text": "for miles down mountainous terrain"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 408789.0,
      "end_time": 411687.0,
      "text": "to trucks waiting at roads below."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 411687.0,
      "end_time": 414205.0,
      "text": "The big sheets of slate were heavier"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 414205.0,
      "end_time": 416871.0,
      "text": "than the children carrying them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 416871.0,
      "end_time": 418900.0,
      "text": "and the kids hoisted them from their heads"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 418900.0,
      "end_time": 423344.0,
      "text": "using these handmade harnesses of sticks and rope"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 423344.0,
      "end_time": 425191.0,
      "text": "and torn cloth."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 425191.0,
      "end_time": 428866.0,
      "text": "It's difficult to witness something so overwhelming."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 428866.0,
      "end_time": 431513.0,
      "text": "How can we affect something so insidious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 431513.0,
      "end_time": 434725.0,
      "text": "yet so pervasive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 434725.0,
      "end_time": 437437.0,
      "text": "Some don't even know they're enslaved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 437437.0,
      "end_time": 442443.0,
      "text": "people working 16, 17 hours a day without any pay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 442443.0,
      "end_time": 445656.0,
      "text": "because this has been the case all their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 445656.0,
      "end_time": 449938.0,
      "text": "They have nothing to compare it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 449938.0,
      "end_time": 453312.0,
      "text": "When these villagers claimed their freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 453312.0,
      "end_time": 458727.0,
      "text": "the slaveholders burned down all of their houses."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 458727.0,
      "end_time": 460689.0,
      "text": "I mean, these people had nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 460689.0,
      "end_time": 464338.0,
      "text": "and they were so petrified, they wanted to give up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 464338.0,
      "end_time": 468385.0,
      "text": "but the woman in the center rallied for them to persevere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 468385.0,
      "end_time": 469881.0,
      "text": "and abolitionists on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 469881.0,
      "end_time": 472540.0,
      "text": "helped them get a quarry lease of their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 472540.0,
      "end_time": 475653.0,
      "text": "so that now they do the same back-breaking work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 475653.0,
      "end_time": 480160.0,
      "text": "but they do it for themselves, and they get paid for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 480160.0,
      "end_time": 483583.0,
      "text": "and they do it in freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 483583.0,
      "end_time": 485651.0,
      "text": "Sex trafficking is what we often think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 485651.0,
      "end_time": 487552.0,
      "text": "when we hear the word slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 487552.0,
      "end_time": 489511.0,
      "text": "and because of this worldwide awareness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 489511.0,
      "end_time": 492647.0,
      "text": "I was warned that it would be difficult for me to work safely"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 492647.0,
      "end_time": 495469.0,
      "text": "within this particular industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 495469.0,
      "end_time": 498311.0,
      "text": "In Kathmandu, I was escorted by women who had"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 498311.0,
      "end_time": 501847.0,
      "text": "previously been sex slaves themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 501847.0,
      "end_time": 504205.0,
      "text": "They ushered me down a narrow set of stairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 504205.0,
      "end_time": 509818.0,
      "text": "that led to this dirty, dimly fluorescent lit basement."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 509818.0,
      "end_time": 511650.0,
      "text": "This wasn't a brothel, per se."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 511650.0,
      "end_time": 513961.0,
      "text": "It was more like a restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 513961.0,
      "end_time": 516221.0,
      "text": "Cabin restaurants, as they're known in the trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 516221.0,
      "end_time": 518843.0,
      "text": "are venues for forced prostitution."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 518842.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521874.99999999994,
      "text": "Each has small, private rooms, where the slaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 521875.0,
      "end_time": 524506.0,
      "text": "women, along with young girls and boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 524506.0,
      "end_time": 527285.0,
      "text": "some as young as seven years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 527285.0,
      "end_time": 529275.0,
      "text": "are forced to entertain the clients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 529275.0,
      "end_time": 533055.0,
      "text": "encouraging them to buy more food and alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 533055.0,
      "end_time": 536094.0,
      "text": "Each cubicle is dark and dingy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 536094.0,
      "end_time": 540033.0,
      "text": "identified with a painted number on the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 540033.0,
      "end_time": 544138.0,
      "text": "and partitioned by plywood and a curtain."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 544138.0,
      "end_time": 547689.0,
      "text": "The workers here often endure tragic sexual abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 547689.0,
      "end_time": 550271.0,
      "text": "at the hands of their customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 550271.0,
      "end_time": 553337.0,
      "text": "Standing in the near darkness, I remember feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 553337.0,
      "end_time": 557423.0,
      "text": "this quick, hot fear, and in that instant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 557423.0,
      "end_time": 559768.0,
      "text": "I could only imagine what it must be like"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 559768.0,
      "end_time": 562431.0,
      "text": "to be trapped in that hell."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 562431.0,
      "end_time": 567033.0,
      "text": "I had only one way out: the stairs from where I'd come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 567033.0,
      "end_time": 568889.0,
      "text": "There were no back doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 568889.0,
      "end_time": 571432.0,
      "text": "There were no windows large enough to climb through."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 571432.0,
      "end_time": 575692.0,
      "text": "These people have no escape at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 575692.0,
      "end_time": 578752.0,
      "text": "and as we take in such a difficult subject,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 578752.0,
      "end_time": 583363.0,
      "text": "it's important to note that slavery, including sex trafficking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 583363.0,
      "end_time": 586292.0,
      "text": "occurs in our own backyard as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 586292.0,
      "end_time": 590916.0,
      "text": "Tens of hundreds of people are enslaved in agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 590916.0,
      "end_time": 593588.0,
      "text": "in restaurants, in domestic servitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 593588.0,
      "end_time": 596220.0,
      "text": "and the list can go on."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 596220.0,
      "end_time": 598859.0,
      "text": "Recently, the New York Times reported that"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 598859.0,
      "end_time": 604665.0,
      "text": "between 100,000 and 300,000 American children"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 604665.0,
      "end_time": 608626.0,
      "text": "are sold into sex slavery every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 608626.0,
      "end_time": 615169.0,
      "text": "It's all around us. We just don't see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 615169.0,
      "end_time": 618551.0,
      "text": "The textile industry is another one we often think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 618551.0,
      "end_time": 621437.0,
      "text": "when we hear about slave labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 621437.0,
      "end_time": 625760.0,
      "text": "I visited villages in India where entire families were enslaved"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 625760.0,
      "end_time": 628405.0,
      "text": "in the silk trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 628405.0,
      "end_time": 630697.0,
      "text": "This is a family portrait."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 630697.0,
      "end_time": 634585.0,
      "text": "The dyed black hands are the father, while the blue"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 634585.0,
      "end_time": 637374.0,
      "text": "and red hands are his sons."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 637374.0,
      "end_time": 640098.0,
      "text": "They mix dye in these big barrels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 640098.0,
      "end_time": 644063.0,
      "text": "and they submerge the silk into the liquid up to their elbows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 644063.0,
      "end_time": 649025.0,
      "text": "but the dye is toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 649025.0,
      "end_time": 652330.0,
      "text": "My interpreter told me their stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 652330.0,
      "end_time": 655932.0,
      "text": "\"We have no freedom,\" they said."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 655932.0,
      "end_time": 659036.0,
      "text": "\"We hope still, though, that we could leave this house"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 659036.0,
      "end_time": 660690.0,
      "text": "someday and go someplace else"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 660690.0,
      "end_time": 667354.0,
      "text": "where we actually get paid for our dyeing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 667354.0,
      "end_time": 672293.0,
      "text": "It's estimated that more than 4,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 672293.0,
      "end_time": 674450.0,
      "text": "are enslaved on Lake Volta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 674450.0,
      "end_time": 678536.0,
      "text": "the largest man-made lake in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 678536.0,
      "end_time": 681510.0,
      "text": "When we first arrived, I went to have a quick look."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 681510.0,
      "end_time": 684878.0,
      "text": "I saw what seemed to be a family fishing on a boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 684878.0,
      "end_time": 689043.0,
      "text": "two older brothers, some younger kids, makes sense right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 689043.0,
      "end_time": 693091.0,
      "text": "Wrong. They were all enslaved."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 693091.0,
      "end_time": 695920.0,
      "text": "Children are taken from their families"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 695920.0,
      "end_time": 698427.0,
      "text": "and trafficked and vanished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 698427.0,
      "end_time": 701339.0,
      "text": "and they're forced to work endless hours on these boats"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 701339.0,
      "end_time": 705886.0,
      "text": "on the lake, even though they do not know how to swim."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 705886.0,
      "end_time": 708221.0,
      "text": "This young child is eight years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 708221.0,
      "end_time": 710877.0,
      "text": "He was trembling when our boat approached,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 710877.0,
      "end_time": 713532.0,
      "text": "frightened it would run over his tiny canoe."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 713532.0,
      "end_time": 716871.0,
      "text": "He was petrified he would be knocked in the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 716871.0,
      "end_time": 720156.0,
      "text": "The skeletal tree limbs submerged in Lake Volta"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 720156.0,
      "end_time": 724121.0,
      "text": "often catch the fishing nets, and weary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 724121.0,
      "end_time": 727854.0,
      "text": "frightened children are thrown into the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 727854.0,
      "end_time": 730005.0,
      "text": "to untether the lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 730005.0,
      "end_time": 732852.0,
      "text": "Many of them drown."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 732852.0,
      "end_time": 736192.0,
      "text": "For as long as he can recall, he's been forced to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 736192.0,
      "end_time": 738365.0,
      "text": "on the lake."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 738365.0,
      "end_time": 741829.0,
      "text": "Terrified of his master, he will not run away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 741829.0,
      "end_time": 745317.0,
      "text": "and since he's been treated with cruelty all his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 745317.0,
      "end_time": 747749.0,
      "text": "he passes that down to the younger slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 747749.0,
      "end_time": 750754.0,
      "text": "that he manages."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 750754.0,
      "end_time": 752858.0,
      "text": "I met these boys at five in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 752858.0,
      "end_time": 755319.0,
      "text": "when they were hauling in the last of their nets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 755319.0,
      "end_time": 758180.0,
      "text": "but they had been working since 1 a.m."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 758180.0,
      "end_time": 761755.0,
      "text": "in the cold, windy night."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 761755.0,
      "end_time": 765021.0,
      "text": "And it's important to note that these nets weigh"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 765021.0,
      "end_time": 769437.0,
      "text": "more than a thousand pounds when they're full of fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 769437.0,
      "end_time": 773940.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce you to Kofi."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 773940.0,
      "end_time": 777186.0,
      "text": "Kofi was rescued from a fishing village."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 777186.0,
      "end_time": 779778.0,
      "text": "I met him at a shelter where Free the Slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 779778.0,
      "end_time": 783707.0,
      "text": "rehabilitates victims of slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 783707.0,
      "end_time": 785788.0,
      "text": "Here he's seen taking a bath at the well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 785788.0,
      "end_time": 788691.0,
      "text": "pouring big buckets of water over his head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 788691.0,
      "end_time": 790612.0,
      "text": "and the wonderful news is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 790612.0,
      "end_time": 792610.0,
      "text": "as you and I are sitting here talking today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 792610.0,
      "end_time": 795845.0,
      "text": "Kofi has been reunited with his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 795845.0,
      "end_time": 798997.0,
      "text": "and what's even better, his family has been given tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 798997.0,
      "end_time": 804724.0,
      "text": "to make a living and to keep their children safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 804724.0,
      "end_time": 809177.0,
      "text": "Kofi is the embodiment of possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 809177.0,
      "end_time": 813748.0,
      "text": "Who will he become because someone took a stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 813748.0,
      "end_time": 817340.0,
      "text": "and made a difference in his life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 817340.0,
      "end_time": 819568.0,
      "text": "Driving down a road in Ghana"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 819568.0,
      "end_time": 821656.0,
      "text": "with partners of Free the Slaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 821656.0,
      "end_time": 824698.0,
      "text": "a fellow abolitionist on a moped suddenly sped up"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 824698.0,
      "end_time": 827645.0,
      "text": "to our cruiser and tapped on the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 827645.0,
      "end_time": 832425.0,
      "text": "He told us to follow him down a dirt road into the jungle."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 832425.0,
      "end_time": 835214.0,
      "text": "At the end of the road, he urged us out of the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 835214.0,
      "end_time": 837893.0,
      "text": "and told the driver to quickly leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 837893.0,
      "end_time": 841238.0,
      "text": "Then he pointed toward this barely visible footpath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 841238.0,
      "end_time": 845135.0,
      "text": "and said, \"This is the path, this is the path. Go.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 845135.0,
      "end_time": 848804.0,
      "text": "As we started down the path, we pushed aside the vines"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 848804.0,
      "end_time": 852604.0,
      "text": "blocking the way, and after about an hour of walking in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 852604.0,
      "end_time": 858130.0,
      "text": "found that the trail had become flooded by recent rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 858130.0,
      "end_time": 859946.0,
      "text": "so I hoisted the photo gear above my head"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 859946.0,
      "end_time": 864532.0,
      "text": "as we descended into these waters up to my chest."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 864532.0,
      "end_time": 868317.0,
      "text": "After another two hours of hiking, the winding trail"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 868317.0,
      "end_time": 872613.0,
      "text": "abruptly ended at a clearing, and before us"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 872613.0,
      "end_time": 874629.0,
      "text": "was a mass of holes"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 874629.0,
      "end_time": 878449.0,
      "text": "that could fit into the size of a football field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 878449.0,
      "end_time": 884043.0,
      "text": "and all of them were full of enslaved people laboring."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 884043.0,
      "end_time": 887188.0,
      "text": "Many women had children strapped to their backs"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 887188.0,
      "end_time": 889228.0,
      "text": "while they were panning for gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 889228.0,
      "end_time": 893531.0,
      "text": "wading in water poisoned by mercury."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 893531.0,
      "end_time": 898409.0,
      "text": "Mercury is used in the extraction process."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 898409.0,
      "end_time": 901565.0,
      "text": "These miners are enslaved in a mine shaft"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 901565.0,
      "end_time": 904639.0,
      "text": "in another part of Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 904639.0,
      "end_time": 907460.0,
      "text": "When they came out of the shaft, they were soaking wet"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 907460.0,
      "end_time": 909738.0,
      "text": "from their own sweat."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 909738.0,
      "end_time": 913741.0,
      "text": "I remember looking into their tired, bloodshot eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 913741.0,
      "end_time": 919482.0,
      "text": "for many of them had been underground for 72 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 919482.0,
      "end_time": 923457.0,
      "text": "The shafts are up to 300 feet deep, and they carry out"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 923457.0,
      "end_time": 927026.0,
      "text": "heavy bags of stone that later will be transported"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 927026.0,
      "end_time": 929627.0,
      "text": "to another area, where the stone will be pounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 929627.0,
      "end_time": 933572.0,
      "text": "so that they can extract the gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 933572.0,
      "end_time": 937677.0,
      "text": "At first glance, the pounding site seems full"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 937677.0,
      "end_time": 942570.0,
      "text": "of powerful men, but when we look closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 942570.0,
      "end_time": 947437.0,
      "text": "we see some less fortunate working on the fringes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 947437.0,
      "end_time": 949580.0,
      "text": "and children too."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 949580.0,
      "end_time": 956722.0,
      "text": "All of them are victim to injury, illness and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 956722.0,
      "end_time": 960702.0,
      "text": "In fact, it's very likely that this muscular person"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 960702.0,
      "end_time": 965237.0,
      "text": "will end up like this one here, racked with tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 965237.0,
      "end_time": 970208.0,
      "text": "and mercury poisoning in just a few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 970208.0,
      "end_time": 974485.0,
      "text": "This is Manuru. When his father died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 974485.0,
      "end_time": 977567.0,
      "text": "his uncle trafficked him to work with him in the mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 977567.0,
      "end_time": 982163.0,
      "text": "When his uncle died, Manuru inherited his uncle's debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 982163.0,
      "end_time": 987105.0,
      "text": "which further forced him into being enslaved in the mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 987105.0,
      "end_time": 989938.0,
      "text": "When I met him, he had been working in the mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 989938.0,
      "end_time": 994731.0,
      "text": "for 14 years, and the leg injury that you see here"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 994731.0,
      "end_time": 996744.0,
      "text": "is actually from a mining accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 996744.0,
      "end_time": 1001861.0,
      "text": "one so severe doctors say his leg should be amputated."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1001880.0,
      "end_time": 1005830.0,
      "text": "On top of that, Manuru has tuberculosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1005830.0,
      "end_time": 1008874.0,
      "text": "yet he's still forced to work day in and day out"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1008870.0,
      "end_time": 1011114.0,
      "text": "in that mine shaft."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1011110.0,
      "end_time": 1016273.0,
      "text": "Even still, he has a dream that he will become free"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1016280.0,
      "end_time": 1019393.0,
      "text": "and become educated with the help of local activists"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1019390.0,
      "end_time": 1021818.0,
      "text": "like Free the Slaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1021820.0,
      "end_time": 1024172.0,
      "text": "and it's this sort of determination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1024170.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1028048.0000000001,
      "text": "in the face of unimaginable odds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1028050.0,
      "end_time": 1035410.0,
      "text": "that fills me with complete awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1035410.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1038710.0000000001,
      "text": "I want to shine a light on slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1038710.0,
      "end_time": 1040965.0,
      "text": "When I was working in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1040960.0,
      "end_time": 1043641.0,
      "text": "I brought lots of candles with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1043650.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1046372.0000000001,
      "text": "and with the help of my interpreter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1046369.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1048686.0,
      "text": "I imparted to the people I was photographing"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1048680.0,
      "end_time": 1051791.0,
      "text": "that I wanted to illuminate their stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1051790.0,
      "end_time": 1053857.0,
      "text": "and their plight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1053860.0,
      "end_time": 1057365.0,
      "text": "so when it was safe for them, and safe for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1057370.0,
      "end_time": 1060711.0,
      "text": "I made these images."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1060710.0,
      "end_time": 1062943.0,
      "text": "They knew their image would be seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1062940.0,
      "end_time": 1064769.0,
      "text": "by you out in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1064770.0,
      "end_time": 1068514.0,
      "text": "I wanted them to know that we will be bearing witness"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1068510.0,
      "end_time": 1072439.0,
      "text": "to them, and that we will do whatever we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1072440.0,
      "end_time": 1077130.0,
      "text": "to help make a difference in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1077130.0,
      "end_time": 1080610.0,
      "text": "I truly believe, if we can see one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1080610.0,
      "end_time": 1085094.0,
      "text": "as fellow human beings, then it becomes very difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1085100.0,
      "end_time": 1090304.0,
      "text": "to tolerate atrocities like slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1090300.0,
      "end_time": 1093984.0,
      "text": "These images are not of issues. They are of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1093980.0,
      "end_time": 1097245.0,
      "text": "real people, like you and me, all deserving"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1097250.0,
      "end_time": 1100730.0,
      "text": "of the same rights, dignity and respect"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1100730.0,
      "end_time": 1102959.0,
      "text": "in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1102960.0,
      "end_time": 1106195.0,
      "text": "There is not a day that goes by that I don't think"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1106190.0,
      "end_time": 1111469.0,
      "text": "of these many beautiful, mistreated people"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1111470.0,
      "end_time": 1116039.0,
      "text": "I've had the tremendous honor of meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1116040.0,
      "end_time": 1119570.0,
      "text": "I hope that these images awaken a force"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1119570.0,
      "end_time": 1122616.0,
      "text": "in those who view them, people like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1122620.0,
      "end_time": 1126896.0,
      "text": "and I hope that force will ignite a fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1126890.0,
      "end_time": 1131813.0,
      "text": "and that fire will shine a light on slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1131820.0,
      "end_time": 1135829.0,
      "text": "for without that light, the beast of bondage"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1135820.0,
      "end_time": 1139004.0,
      "text": "can continue to live in the shadows."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1139010.0,
      "end_time": 1141987.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1141990.0,
      "end_time": 1155243.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}